This document outlines the Software Requirements Specification (SRS) for the E-Classroom Website, a web-based platform designed to enhance online education for students, teachers, and administrators. The system provides features for virtual classroom management, assignment handling, resource sharing, communication, and performance tracking. Built using React.js, Node.js, and SQL, the platform aims to be secure, scalable, and user-friendly.
