1. Introduction

The E-Classroom Website is a web-based platform designed to support online learning for schools, colleges, and training institutes. It enables teachers and students to interact using virtual classes, assignments, and real-time communication tools.
The system includes:

Class creation & management

Study material upload

Assignment submission and grading

Real-time communication

User role-based access and dashboards


Developed using React.js, Tailwind CSS, HTML, CSS, Node.js, and SQL, the system ensures a scalable and flexible environment for modern online education.


---

1.1 Purpose

The purpose of this system is to:

Provide a digital platform for teachers and students

Support assignment management, resource sharing, and communication

Ensure secure data handling using SQL

Improve accessibility and efficiency in remote education

Provide a responsive interface with React.js and Tailwind CSS



