1.4 User Characteristics

Admin

Manages all users

Monitors system performance

Has full access rights


Teacher

Creates and manages classes

Uploads materials

Grades assignments

Communicates with students


Student

Enrolls in classes

Views materials

Submits assignments

Engages in discussions


Guest (Optional)

View limited public information only



