1.5 Similar Apps and Systems

1. Google Classroom

Pros: User-friendly, assignment workflow
Cons: Limited customization, no deep analytics

2. Moodle

Pros: Open-source, customizable
Cons: Complex for new users

3. Edmodo

Pros: Social learning features
Cons: Not ideal for higher education


