---

FR004 â€“ Upload Course Material

Teacher uploads files (PDF, Video, Word) with description.

Output: Material available to students.


---

FR005 â€“ Submit Assignment

Students upload assignment files with optional comments.

Output: Submission saved for teacher review.


---

