2.2 Non-Functional Requirements

Performance

Supports 500+ concurrent users

Page loads < 3 seconds

Queries < 2 seconds


Scalability

Must support increase in users and courses


Security

Password encryption

HTTPS enforced

Role-based access control


Usability

Complete major tasks within three clicks

Clean UI for easy navigation


Availability

99.5% uptime


Compatibility

Runs on Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge

Responsive on mobile and desktop


Maintainability

Modular code

Proper documentation


Backup & Recovery

Daily automatic backups

Recovery within 1 hour



