3. Use Cases & Flow of Processes

UC-1: Login

Actors: Teacher, Student, Parent
Trigger: User opens app
Description: User logs into the system
Normal Flow:

1. Open login page


2. Enter email and password


3. System validates


4. User dashboard opens




---

UC-2: Manage User Accounts

Actor: Admin
Description: Admin creates, edits, or deletes accounts


---

UC-3: Record Attendance

Actor: Teacher
Description: Teacher marks students present/absent/tardy


---

UC-4: View Attendance Reports

Actors: Teacher, Student, Parent
Description: View attendance history


---

UC-5: Receive Attendance Notifications

Actor: Parent
Description: System sends absence/tardy alerts


